{
  "texts": [
    "The salient targets of the track are social networks and real-time search.",
    "The TREC 2011 Microblog Tracks contains 50 queries and approximately 16 million tweets sampled from January 23 to February 8, 2011, from Twitter.",
    "For TREC 2012, the organizers used a new set of 60 topics and the same corpus as that of TREC 2011.",
    "TREC 2013 consists of 60 4 https://github.com/cdegroc/warc-clueweb queries and approximately 240M tweets collected from Twitter from February 1 to March 31, 2013.",
    "TREC 2014 contains a set of 55 queries and the same collection as TREC 2013.4.2 Resources for BERT-based Ranking ModelMatchZoo 5 is a text-matching toolkit that focuses on developing text-matching models."
  ]
}